  "text": "Posterior pituitary slices. Mouse posterior pituitary slices were prepared by the same procedures used for rat [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We cut 70-mm-thick slices with a vibratome at B0 1C and maintained them in ice-cold artificial cerebrospinal fluid consisting of 125 mM NaCl, 4 mM KCl, 1.25 mM NaH 2 PO 4 , 26 mM NaHCO 3 , 2 mM CaCl 2 and 1 mM MgCl 2 bubbled with 95% O 2 /5% CO 2 .",
